text.section:
Sales and deliveries of distilled spirits and wine may be made at wholesale, and from the licensed premises only:
By distillers to rectifiers, wineries, holders of special nonbeverage alcohol licenses so far as they may make the purchases, or other distillers;
By rectifiers to wineries or to distillers if distilled spirits sold to distillers are packaged in retail containers;
By wineries to rectifiers or other wineries, or to the holders of special nonbeverage alcohol licenses;
By distillers, rectifiers, or wineries to wholesalers; or
By distillers, rectifiers, or wineries for export out of the state.
